{"tid":659635,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"感動！費格遜甦醒就問足球 想看C.朗踢歐聯決賽","createTime":"2018-05-10T04:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:37:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd05581aa3d824f6f31e85c755a988845ea2705","tid":659635,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"曼聯傳奇教練費格遜爵士近日因為突發腦溢血接受了手術，如今費sir還在重症監護中。不過來自《太陽報》的消息稱，費sir術後甦醒後的精神狀態很好，家人很受鼓舞，他醒來後談的話題還是足球。<br />\n<br />\n費sir緊急入院的當天，他的兒子達倫-費格遜所執教的球隊唐卡士打將迎來和韋根的比賽，那也是賽季的最後一戰。費sir因病沒有看到比賽的情況。《太陽報》稱，費sir醒來後的第一句話就是&lsquo;唐卡士打的比賽怎麼樣了？&rsquo;身邊的人稱：「這就是典型的費格遜爵士，永遠不能停止談論足球。」<br />\n<br />\n《太陽報》報導，費格遜爵士想要去溫布萊現場觀看曼聯和車路士的足總盃決賽，但是他也很不情願的承認，自己的身體狀況很難趕上那場比賽。費sir還和家人開玩笑：「啊，足總盃決賽不行，那麼去基輔（歐聯決賽）行嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n曼聯內部消息透露：「費格遜當然想在5月26日去基輔看C.朗拿度皇馬對陣利物浦的比賽。C.朗拿度將費格遜看做是父親般的人物，但是費格遜爵士需要很多時間來休養，他必須嚴格遵守醫生的只是才能完全恢復。<br />\n<br />\n目前看來，費sir的恢復狀態還是不錯的。《太陽報》稱費格遜的家人如今都在身邊陪著他，對於他的恢復進展，家人們都感到很受鼓舞。"},{"pid":"4b2b81f303e2395fb98d73c7e2f8fc847bb83242","tid":659635,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓主今次醒唔加句括號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5601a34df468635c52cf823aa01aee676135b26","tid":659635,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2b81f303e2395fb98d73c7e2f8fc847bb83242","tid":659635,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓主今次醒唔加句括號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f59ee6a20ed356cd417cdcba4a37cbfdffc6f72","tid":659635,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  教練 我好想打。。"},{"pid":"72e8aeb0536f4304772b55d2f32c43534b921435","tid":659635,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"費sir真係當丙朗係仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f2483b70624f5f821c585911be72f15accae7d","tid":659635,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"希望費蛇早日康復"},{"pid":"c1ebeafe3110d58d7b944d2eb7dca5a073c6f6ee","tid":659635,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5601a34df468635c52cf823aa01aee676135b26","tid":659635,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2b81f303e2395fb98d73c7e2f8fc847bb83242","tid":659635,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓主今次醒唔加句括號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}